title: CeeLo's Grammy Outfit Looks Like a Lot of Things
text:
CeeLo's Grammy Outfit Looks Like a Lot of Things By Facebook Frazer Harrison 
In the past, we've given entertainer and musician Cee-Lo Green a pass for his increasingly out-there oufits. In fact, we'e created an honor just for his unique blend of maximalism and DGAF-nessâ€”the You Do You Award . 
But then Green rolled up to the 2017 Grammys in his newest musical incarnation Gnarly Davidson and well, the look was definitely statement-making. As to what that statement was, however, is up to your interpretation. Was he a gold-dipped Samurai? A 'roided-out C-3PO? A Hatchimal someone didn't want? We're not entirely sure, and the internet seems to agree, albeit with some helpful suggestions:
